04:06.794 --> 04:17.687
bomber, a fighter bomber, misidentifying the 
target, or maybe even missing the target, and

04:06.794 --> 04:17.687
screwing his bomb across the city. 
Understandable era, definitely not

04:18.768 --> 04:26.538
intentional, but generally that's what it was. I 
